headline: Kimco's Q3 FFO & Revenues Beat Estimates, Dividend Raised
summary: KIM posts solid Q3 results, with higher FFO per share and revenues, boosted by rising rents and occupancy and lifts its dividend and 2025 FFO per share outlook.

headline: Public Storage's Q3 FFO & Revenues Beat Estimates, '25 View Raised
summary: PSA posts higher Q3 FFO and revenues, fueled by rent gains and acquisitions, and lifts its 2025 outlook on stabilizing operations.
